Class: Theme

insight. Theme

new insight.Theme()

The Theme base class provides the basic structure of a theme, to allow the Chart, Series or Axis to extract values from it to style themselves. All values are `undefined`, being properly set in the subclasses of Theme.

Members

The styles to apply to an axis.
Properties:
Name Type Description

tickSize Integer The length of axis ticks, in pixels.
tickPadding Integer The distance between the end of axis tick marks and tick labels, in pixels.
tickLineWidth Integer The width of the tick marks, in pixels.
tickLineColor Color The color of the tick marks.
axisLineWidth Integer The width of the axis line, in pixels.
axisLineColor Color The color of an axis line.
tickLabelFont Font The font to use for axis tick labels.
tickLabelColor Color The color to use for axis tick labels.
axisTitleFont Font The font to use for an axis title.
axisTitleColor Color The color to use for an axis title.

Name Type Description

The styles to apply to a series
Properties:
Name Type Description
